                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Facts by our side<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 are never sudden </l>
                    <l>Until they look<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 around </l>
                    <l>And then they<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 scare us like a<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 spectre </l>
                    <l>Protruding from<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 the Ground - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The hight of our<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
<add type="alternate" extent="portentous">unknowing</add>
 portentous Neighbor</l>
                    <l>We never know - </l>
                    <l>Till summoned<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 to his recognition </l>
                    <l>By an Adieu - </l>
                    <l>Adieu<add type="alternate" extent="for whence">till when</add>
 for whence<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 the<add type="alternate" extent="sage">wise</add>
 sage cannot<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Conjecture<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                    <l>The bravest die</l>
                    <l>As ignorant of<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 their resumption </l>
                    <l>As<add type="alternate" extent="you or I -">Cowards do -</add>
 you or I - </l>
                </lg>

